you are indeed better than your useless father
in terms of ability though you are young.

77
00:06:45,133 --> 00:06:46,266
But, boy,

78
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:49,033
your father is smarter than you.

79
00:06:50,366 --> 00:06:51,500
This time

80
00:06:52,666 --> 00:06:54,466
