121
00:09:44,666 --> 00:09:45,966
You injured Zhang Yanze.

122
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,666
So what?

123
00:09:49,733 --> 00:09:50,633
Hongchu,

124
00:09:51,866 --> 00:09:55,700
