125
00:09:57,266 --> 00:09:59,100
This is people's support.

126
00:10:03,300 --> 00:10:07,366
Do you know for what Minister Sang
choose to sacrificed in Kaifeng?

127
00:10:08,833 --> 00:10:09,700
For people's support.

128
00:10:11,133 --> 00:10:15,733
Minister Sang used his life to let the Khitan ruler know

129
00:10:17,266 --> 00:10:18,966
