00:11:32,766 --> 00:11:35,033
[Shi Hongzhao, Military Commander of Hedong]
After all, Lord Feng had no troops in hand;

145
00:11:35,033 --> 00:11:38,733
[Shi Hongzhao, Military Commander of Hedong]
