00:17:21,866 --> 00:17:26,360
Lord Liu is granted the title of Grand Preceptor and
Prince of Jin to eternally guard Hedong.

245
00:17:48,766 --> 00:17:49,433
Your Majesty.

246
00:18:04,266 --> 00:18:04,833
Fan Zhi.

247
00:18:06,500 --> 00:18:07,166
Yes.

248
00:18:07,733 --> 00:18:12,400
Instruct the Kaifeng Prefecture to set up
two more porridge kitchens in the southern city.

249
00:18:13,433 --> 00:18:15,233
Do not use the name of relief aid.

250
00:18:16,233 --> 00:18:20,866
The weather is about to turn warm and
ice in the river will soon melt.

251
00:18:21,700 --> 00:18:25,900
Recruit strong and young men and provide relief through work.

252
00:18:27,433 --> 00:18:27,866
Yes.

253
00:18:44,866 --> 00:18:45,466
My apologize.

254
00:18:46,433 --> 00:18:47,000
Lord.

255
00:18:48,433 --> 00:18:49,700
Accompany me for a walk.

256
00:18:54,500 --> 00:18:55,866
You can get it there as well.

257
00:18:55,866 --> 00:18:56,466
Thanks.

258
00:18:57,266 --> 00:18:58,300
Give me more.

259
00:18:59,300 --> 00:19:02,000
I'm afraid there are a hundred thousand people.

260
00:19:02,833 --> 00:19:05,000
There are not so many.

261
00:19:05,833 --> 00:19:11,066
In the twelve counties of the capital region, only
Chenliu's city walls are still somewhat intact.

262
00:19:12,766 --> 00:19:13,833
But no one remains there.

263
00:19:15,400 --> 00:19:18,233
The weather is bitterly cold, the ground frozen.

264
00:19:18,233 --> 00:19:22,866
Poor families runing out of food can only leave their homes,

265
00:19:24,233 --> 00:19:27,466
heading towards the capital to beg for some food.

266
00:19:28,933 --> 00:19:29,466
This

267
00:19:31,033 --> 00:19:32,500
is only just the beginning.

268
00:19:33,733 --> 00:19:34,300
Why?

269
00:19:35,200 --> 00:19:37,633
The weather is gradually warming up.

270
00:19:37,633 --> 00:19:39,133
In past years at this time,

271
00:19:39,766 --> 00:19:43,433
the court would have allocated seed grain
to prepare for spring plowing.

272
00:19:44,933 --> 00:19:50,233
This year the stored grain in the
government granaries and seed grain

273
00:19:51,133 --> 00:19:53,633
have all eaten by the soldiers and refugees.

274
00:19:55,300 --> 00:20:00,133
We miss the farming season, and
there will be no hope for a harvest.

275
00:20:01,933 --> 00:20:03,033
These common people,

276
00:20:04,600 --> 00:20:05,233
for now,

277
00:20:06,566 --> 00:20:10,366
can still come here to beg for some porridge and barely get by.

278
00:20:11,400 --> 00:20:15,600
In another two months, when the granary reserves
are all eaten up,

279
00:20:16,700 --> 00:20:21,500
they will ultimately starve to death.

280
00:20:22,833 --> 00:20:24,466
Lord oversees affairs in this city.

281
00:20:27,300 --> 00:20:29,300
Isn't this within your responsibilities?

282
00:20:31,733 --> 00:20:32,366
I am ashamed.

283
00:20:33,766 --> 00:20:35,833
But I cannot make bricks without straw.

284
00:20:36,966 --> 00:20:40,300
The reserves of the inner and outer treasuries
are all in your hands, Lord.

285
00:20:41,600 --> 00:20:42,766
What else do you need?

286
00:20:43,400 --> 00:20:43,933
I am

287
00:20:45,400 --> 00:20:46,933
just a muddle-headed old fool.

288
00:20:47,966 --> 00:20:49,800
For food, a single bowl is enough.

289
00:20:50,566 --> 00:20:52,733
To sleep, a simple bed suffices.

290
00:20:53,366 --> 00:20:54,766
I need nothing else.

291
00:20:57,566 --> 00:20:58,666
They need something.

292
00:21:00,866 --> 00:21:01,766
They need something.

293
00:21:03,133 --> 00:21:03,866
Need what?

294
00:21:04,766 --> 00:21:06,066
A proper court.

295
00:21:07,566 --> 00:21:11,566
One that can purchase grain at fair prices in harvest years,

296
00:21:12,300 --> 00:21:15,966
distribute food and provide relief in famine years.

297
00:21:17,033 --> 00:21:20,900
One that allocates seed grain in spring,

298
00:21:21,633 --> 00:21:24,100
repairs river infrastructure in summer ,

299
00:21:24,833 --> 00:21:26,966
fills granaries in autumn,

300
00:21:27,333 --> 00:21:31,000
and relieves the cold and needy in winter.

301
00:21:35,700 --> 00:21:42,833
Today not even a Bodhisattva
can keep these common people alive.

302
00:21:45,133 --> 00:21:46,200
Only you

303
00:21:47,800 --> 00:21:49,133
can keep them alive.

304
00:21:50,533 --> 00:21:52,166
Lord, are those your sincere words?

305
00:21:53,366 --> 00:21:54,900
Can you?

306
00:22:01,933 --> 00:22:02,800
Zhang Li.

307
00:22:03,966 --> 00:22:05,633
I am here.

308
00:22:06,233 --> 00:22:09,733
Announce to all palace camps and to ministers:

309
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:14,833
From this day forth, south of the great river,
no one shall plunder the commoners.

310
00:22:15,833 --> 00:22:22,566
All military needs must be recorded in writing, compiled
into registers, and submitted to the palace for decision.

311
00:22:22,833 --> 00:22:24,466
I receive the decree.

312
00:22:25,600 --> 00:22:26,200
Lord,

313
00:22:28,466 --> 00:22:29,500
is this acceptable?

314
00:22:34,366 --> 00:22:35,930
Rioting troops entered the city,

315
00:22:37,100 --> 00:22:38,166
giving three days' leave.

316
00:22:38,866 --> 00:22:41,366
let the strong broke down doors,

317
00:22:43,166 --> 00:22:45,933
plundering coins, silk, and rations,

318
00:22:46,400 --> 00:22:49,433
slaughtering women and children,

319
00:22:50,933 --> 00:22:52,533
setting houses ablaze,

320
00:22:52,633 --> 00:22:55,033
tearing down courtyard walls to build camps...

321
00:22:55,100 --> 00:22:55,633
Lord,

322
00:22:58,633 --> 00:23:00,433
is this the crime of Zhang Yanze,

323
00:23:02,866 --> 00:23:03,766
or of me?

324
00:23:04,966 --> 00:23:06,166
You've using too heavy words.

325
00:23:06,833 --> 00:23:07,266
But

326
00:23:08,100 --> 00:23:09,033
at this moment,

327
00:23:10,466 --> 00:23:14,900
with you simply saying "No more plundering, no more killing,"

328
00:23:16,433 --> 00:23:17,500
will that suffice?

329
00:23:23,366 --> 00:23:24,700
What exactly do you want?

330
00:23:25,366 --> 00:23:27,900
Three hundred thousand hu of grain and wheat

331
00:23:28,566 --> 00:23:30,300
thirty thousand hu of seed grain,

332
00:23:31,433 --> 00:23:32,133
Do you have them?

333
00:23:32,766 --> 00:23:33,300
No.

334
00:23:34,100 --> 00:23:38,200
Since you do not, the hundred thousand
soldiers and civilians here and I

335
00:23:39,000 --> 00:23:41,266
cannot let you do something you can't.

336
00:23:42,866 --> 00:23:43,333
But

337
00:23:45,133 --> 00:23:46,800
we can settle for the next best thing.

338
00:23:46,800 --> 00:23:47,666
What is it?

339
00:23:48,300 --> 00:23:52,066
Debts must be repaid, lives taken must be atoned for.

340
00:23:54,366 --> 00:23:57,233
Since you have no grain or seed,

341
00:23:58,733 --> 00:24:02,966
you may instead offer Zhang Yanze's life in compensation.

342
00:24:03,400 --> 00:24:05,733
Lord Feng, you are threatening His Majesty?

343
00:24:06,866 --> 00:24:07,830
Your Majesty,

344
00:24:09,300 --> 00:24:12,666
if you do that, Du Zhongwei may incite unforeseen turmoil.

345
00:24:15,200 --> 00:24:16,100
That's reasonable.

346
00:24:17,433 --> 00:24:20,066
Du Zhongwei holds heavy troops.

347
00:24:20,466 --> 00:24:23,066
Even Bodhisattva won't defy him, let alone you.

348
00:24:25,566 --> 00:24:27,100
Is this your intention,

349
00:24:29,966 --> 00:24:32,200
or Liu Zhiyuan of Taiyuan's intention?

350
00:24:32,633 --> 00:24:35,166
If you are unwilling to be the ruler,

351
00:24:36,433 --> 00:24:40,866
then move back to your Shangjing immediately.

352
00:24:41,300 --> 00:24:43,333
Lord, you have not yet answered.

353
00:24:50,100 --> 00:24:51,600
A person who cares for the world

354
00:24:53,400 --> 00:24:55,066
would not ask such a question.

355
00:25:01,200 --> 00:25:03,600
If I kill Zhang Yanze,

356
00:25:06,700 --> 00:25:09,566
dare you guarantee that Du Zhongwei will not rebel?

357
00:25:10,000 --> 00:25:10,633
I dare not.

358
00:25:12,733 --> 00:25:13,166
But

359
00:25:14,966 --> 00:25:16,233
I dare wager.

360
00:25:18,400 --> 00:25:19,266
Du Zhongwei

361
00:25:20,400 --> 00:25:21,333
is in Yexia.

362
00:25:22,233 --> 00:25:24,433
I am in the capital,

363
00:25:25,533 --> 00:25:26,133
with no city,

364
00:25:26,766 --> 00:25:27,333
no troops.

365
00:25:28,033 --> 00:25:29,633
If Du Zhongwei dares to rebel,

366
00:25:30,766 --> 00:25:32,266
you may just take

367
00:25:33,200 --> 00:25:34,366
my life.

368
00:25:39,200 --> 00:25:40,100
Dare you wager?

369
00:25:41,866 --> 00:25:46,133
The authorities have investigated the crimes of Zhang Yanze.

370
00:25:46,333 --> 00:25:49,000
Zhang is greedy and covetous, plundering people.

371
00:25:49,500 --> 00:25:52,666
He has been ruthlessly killing civilians at will.

372
00:25:52,666 --> 00:25:55,166
He allows soldiers' atrocities, people suffering.

373
00:25:55,766 --> 00:25:59,066
He embezzles military pay,
leading to the army's morale collapsing.

374
00:25:59,066 --> 00:26:02,433
He seizes farmland and deprived people of their property,

375
00:26:02,433 --> 00:26:05,866
He also sells official positions, corrupting governance.

376
00:26:05,866 --> 00:26:08,433
He drives soldiers to rebel, causing disasters.

377
00:26:09,266 --> 00:26:12,866
He defies imperial decrees, disobeying the emperor's orders.

378
00:26:12,866 --> 00:26:15,533
He frames loyal officials, persecuting the virtuous.

379
00:26:16,133 --> 00:26:18,900
He indulges in lechery, corrupting social morals.

380
00:26:19,900 --> 00:26:22,500
He forms cliques, disrupting court order.

381
00:26:23,033 --> 00:26:26,433
He robs and kills envoys, provoking neighboring states.

382
00:26:26,433 --> 00:26:27,866
These are twelve major crimes.

383
00:26:27,866 --> 00:26:31,200
His crimes is too many to be each listed and recorded.

384
00:26:31,733 --> 00:26:33,233
Even drained the Sea,

385
00:26:33,566 --> 00:26:35,400
his evil can't be washed away.

386
00:26:35,866 --> 00:26:39,966
to such a great villain, how could I
spare him from the punishments?

387
00:26:40,566 --> 00:26:44,300
He shall be immediately caged and sent to the market
to be publicly executed,

388
00:26:44,733 --> 00:26:48,566
to serve as a warning, proclaimed to all.

389
00:26:49,733 --> 00:26:50,333
Lord

390
00:26:51,400 --> 00:26:52,366
Zhang Yanze

391
00:26:53,333 --> 00:26:58,900
was executed under the clear edict of the Khitan emperor,
publicly executed according to the law.

392
00:26:59,666 --> 00:27:02,466
people of Bianliang City are all witnesses.

393
00:27:03,666 --> 00:27:05,166
In the clear annals of history,

394
00:27:06,533 --> 00:27:08,366
it will be recorded thus in the future.

395
00:27:10,333 --> 00:27:12,033
What a pity for Qian's Young Master,

396
00:27:12,700 --> 00:27:13,766
so loyal and brave.

397
00:27:14,400 --> 00:27:15,660
In these chaotic times,

398
00:27:17,933 --> 00:27:19,333
human life is cheap.

399
00:27:20,733 --> 00:27:21,400
Staying alive,

400
00:27:23,000 --> 00:27:25,260
is more important than anything else.

401
00:27:26,433 --> 00:27:27,533
Should we release him?

402
00:27:28,533 --> 00:27:29,133
Not yet.

403
00:27:29,900 --> 00:27:32,666
Disrespect in court is not minor offense.

404
00:27:35,066 --> 00:27:36,366
Take good care of him.

405
00:27:37,666 --> 00:27:39,500
Do not let anyone see him,

406
00:27:40,100 --> 00:27:41,700
and do not let anyone

407
00:27:43,000 --> 00:27:44,166
be reminded of him.

408
00:28:01,500 --> 00:28:02,966
It's roasting so slowly.

409
00:28:13,300 --> 00:28:14,800
What are you thinking about again?

410
00:28:21,666 --> 00:28:23,333
If I survive and return this time,

411
00:28:25,133 --> 00:28:30,533
I will go to the island with you and become a live-in son-in-law.

412
00:28:30,900 --> 00:28:31,466
Okay?

413
00:28:35,233 --> 00:28:37,560
What nonsense are you talking about?

414
00:28:41,900 --> 00:28:42,966
In this world,

415
00:28:43,600 --> 00:28:51,133
there are too many people who want to shoulder
great responsibilities, but too few with self-awareness.

416
00:28:53,166 --> 00:28:54,200
Otherwise,

417
00:28:55,933 --> 00:28:57,733
it wouldn't have been this chaotic.

418
00:29:01,666 --> 00:29:02,900
I won't get involved.

419
00:29:03,700 --> 00:29:05,133
After much thought,

420
00:29:06,266 --> 00:29:11,033
this world seems to have no second Arcadia
besides Huanglong Island.

421
00:29:28,366 --> 00:29:29,033
Do you

422
00:29:30,766 --> 00:29:31,833
really think so?

423
00:29:54,400 --> 00:29:55,066
What do you think?

424
00:30:06,933 --> 00:30:07,433
Lord,

425
00:30:10,766 --> 00:30:11,200
Lord,

426
00:30:12,100 --> 00:30:14,966
Wang Jun, the envoy from Taiyuan, requests an audience.

427
00:30:14,966 --> 00:30:16,033
He's finally here.

428
00:30:16,566 --> 00:30:17,530
I won't see him.

429
00:30:18,366 --> 00:30:19,033
Lord.

430
00:30:20,533 --> 00:30:21,133
Fan Zhi,

431
00:30:22,300 --> 00:30:23,500
you go meet him.

432
00:30:24,233 --> 00:30:25,900
Wang Jun wants to see you, Lord,

433
00:30:26,233 --> 00:30:27,066
not me.

434
00:30:28,333 --> 00:30:29,933
Everything that can be asked and said,

435
00:30:31,133 --> 00:30:35,333
I have discussed with that Guo boy.

436
00:30:36,166 --> 00:30:39,233
Meeting again wih him would just be repeating the same words.

437
00:30:40,266 --> 00:30:41,166
Better not to meet.

438
00:30:42,066 --> 00:30:42,966
You go see him.

439
00:30:44,100 --> 00:30:44,800
Tell him:

440
00:30:45,766 --> 00:30:50,666
millet and wheat, six million liters each,
and six hundred thousand liters of seed.

441
00:30:51,733 --> 00:30:54,233
This is the price I offer.

442
00:30:56,966 --> 00:30:57,966
This world,

443
00:30:59,733 --> 00:31:00,600
at present,

444
00:31:02,100 --> 00:31:03,533
is only worth this much.

445
00:31:04,866 --> 00:31:06,933
Lord is a senior minister of three dynasties.

446
00:31:07,700 --> 00:31:09,166
Why be so discourteous?

447
00:31:10,533 --> 00:31:12,366
Xiufeng, be careful with your words.

448
00:31:13,500 --> 00:31:15,633
Lord leads the court.

449
00:31:16,400 --> 00:31:19,733
His thoughts and actions are not for us to comment on.

450
00:31:20,600 --> 00:31:22,933
The humiliation of you and your Lord today,

451
00:31:24,233 --> 00:31:25,333
I will

452
00:31:26,266 --> 00:31:27,733
surely repay it someday.

453
00:31:34,866 --> 00:31:36,100
Lord refuses to see me.

454
00:31:37,966 --> 00:31:38,433
Yes.

455
00:31:40,433 --> 00:31:41,633
His exact words were:

456
00:31:43,533 --> 00:31:44,000
"If he

457
00:31:45,566 --> 00:31:46,833
still cherishes his life,

458
00:31:47,266 --> 00:31:50,033
he should not go anywhere these days ."

459
00:31:54,733 --> 00:31:56,266
Please inform the Lord, Marshal.

460
00:31:56,266 --> 00:31:58,900
Guo Rong has a few heartfelt words for him.

461
00:31:59,833 --> 00:32:01,866
This concerns his reputation.

462
00:32:02,366 --> 00:32:04,530
I beg him to spare some time for a meeting.

463
00:32:08,600 --> 00:32:09,700
Just give up.

464
00:32:10,733 --> 00:32:13,666
Tomorrow, at the grand court assembly in Hall,

465
00:32:15,233 --> 00:32:19,166
he will go to the hall and declare submission.

466
00:32:22,900 --> 00:32:25,366
The Great Khitan Emperor decrees:

467
00:32:26,100 --> 00:32:29,666
By the grace of Heaven, I have ascended to throne.

468
00:32:30,200 --> 00:32:36,066
To govern the great realm, it's necessary
to have virtuous ministers to assist.

469
00:32:36,533 --> 00:32:39,366
You, Marshal, Director of the Secretariat,

470
00:32:39,833 --> 00:32:43,566
Military Governor of Kuangguo Weisheng Army, Duke of Yan,

471
00:32:43,600 --> 00:32:47,833
having served three dynasties with
splendid knowledge and reputation,

472
00:32:47,833 --> 00:32:49,833
as a crucial minister to the state,

473
00:32:50,300 --> 00:32:55,200
are hereby appointed Grand Tutor, recorded with
a golden register, and granted Prince of Changle.

474
00:32:55,200 --> 00:32:59,433
There's another eight thousand households for you as fief,
twelve hundred to be taxed,

475
00:32:59,433 --> 00:33:03,530
You shall serve as Military Commissioner,
overseeing affairs of the Southern Han Office,

476
00:33:03,530 --> 00:33:05,333
commanding the troops of Bianliang.

477
00:33:05,566 --> 00:33:08,000
You shall be granted an ivory tablet and an ox-head token,

478
00:33:08,566 --> 00:33:11,933
permitted to ride a horse within the palace and attend court,

479
00:33:13,033 --> 00:33:13,966
Approved.

480
00:33:19,400 --> 00:33:23,200
Your subject, Feng Dao, receives the decree.

481
00:33:25,866 --> 00:33:31,733
Having obtained the great succession, I would trouble you
as to the matter of the dynastic name.

482
00:33:32,433 --> 00:33:36,133
The Yang clan obtained the succession as Duke of Sui,

483
00:33:36,233 --> 00:33:38,100
the dynastic name was Sui.

484
00:33:38,100 --> 00:33:40,766
The Li clan obtained the succession as Duke of Tang,

485
00:33:41,433 --> 00:33:44,300
thus establishing the Tang of three hundred years.

486
00:33:44,933 --> 00:33:48,533
Your Majesty's foundation was obtained
from your father and grandfather.

487
00:33:48,533 --> 00:33:52,866
The ancestral temples and shrines,
though not granted by Tang decree,

488
00:33:53,200 --> 00:33:57,566
follow the old system of the Songmo Governorate.

489
00:33:58,233 --> 00:34:01,366
Songmo had its governance in Liao territory.

490
00:34:02,400 --> 00:34:06,633
For Your Majesty to name the state, the name could be Liao.

491
00:34:41,133 --> 00:34:41,833
Liao.

492
00:34:45,066 --> 00:34:46,266
Great Liao.

493
00:34:48,800 --> 00:34:50,866
Grand Tutor's proposal fits the traditions.

494
00:34:51,600 --> 00:34:54,566
I concur that the state name shall be Liao.

495
00:34:55,133 --> 00:34:56,600
I concur!

496
00:34:56,700 --> 00:34:57,133
Good.

497
00:34:58,166 --> 00:35:01,400
Then the state name is settled, Liao.

498
00:35:02,066 --> 00:35:03,600
May our ancestors bless us.

499
00:35:03,600 --> 00:35:05,500
May the Great Liao prosper forever.

500
00:35:05,500 --> 00:35:08,000
Long live Your Majesty.

501
00:35:10,666 --> 00:35:12,366
May the Great Liao prosper forever.

502
00:35:12,800 --> 00:35:15,400
Long live Your Majesty.

503
00:35:21,366 --> 00:35:25,733
A senior minister of three dynasties bowed in submission
,even offering a state name.

504
00:35:27,200 --> 00:35:28,400
Truly beyond my words.

505
00:35:30,000 --> 00:35:36,566
I wonders will Lord Feng feel ashamed the day he
meet Minister Sang again in the underworld.

506
00:35:37,166 --> 00:35:38,566
If Minister Sang had not died,

507
00:35:39,600 --> 00:35:42,133
Today, I'm afraid he too would have submitted.

508
00:35:43,633 --> 00:35:47,033
The Han culture has been moved to south for seven hundred years.

